SEED — Typed Project Incubator
Source: https://github.com/ChristopherKahler/seed.git
Type: external_tool
Category: workflow / ideation
Version: 0.1.3
Author: Chris Kahler (same as PAUL)
Cloned to: ~/claude-hq/repos/seed/
Install: npm i -g @chrisai/seed
Key files: seed.md (entry point), tasks/ (5 task files), data/ (5 type configs), templates/ (5 PLANNING.md templates), checklists/ (quality gate)
Commands: /seed, /seed graduate, /seed launch, /seed status, /seed add-type
Project types: Application (deep), Workflow (standard), Client (standard), Utility (tight), Campaign (creative)
PAUL integration: /seed launch → graduates plan → headless PAUL init from PLANNING.md
